{"tid":294070,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"隻腳板底甩皮係咩一回事？","createTime":"2017-06-22T15:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T02:54:28.000Z","uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23df96fe2a39999b71ae3efb8de596950c8e88ba","tid":294070,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"暫時又唔覺佢痕，淨係會係咁甩皮，強迫症咁會想整甩佢<br />\n冇圖，費事嚇親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有人想睇再貼"},{"pid":"62bea5e7424e31f0b6cc23f31d9ac224fc5af3a1","tid":294070,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"香港地有香港腳"},{"pid":"0af2b8e859db80884a36c2bb80fe5ac57b07be0c","tid":294070,"uid":31109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"有朋友都係咁"},{"pid":"25ffc81e45cccf390f7a5d03c46385f0552396e7","tid":294070,"uid":31145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"甩完就冇事 上次我都係咁<br />\n摵出黎個下好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8959ccce7183b9d187f6cf69950f254339907312","tid":294070,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地有香港腳</blockquote><br />\n但唔覺有痕，咁都係香港腳？"},{"pid":"83452ca1d0c188fd21e4614e68fd487da731cb09","tid":294070,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友都係咁</blockquote><br />\n有冇用咩藥好返？"},{"pid":"b63257785944fb7b01fa95f05858419b23314abd","tid":294070,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甩完就冇事 上次我都係咁<br />\n摵出黎個下好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n的確係好爽嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86146e2c570c267e9aa5c627cb785151b578339e","tid":294070,"uid":32552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"平時著住鞋襪太焗 <br />\n通爽d就唔會甩咁多<br />\n想mit都最好沖完熱水涼 啲皮軟少少先慢慢捽甩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703fd18d55ef0128fd98e4dbe7104bc7b832c7d3","tid":294070,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時著住鞋襪太焗 <br />\n通爽d就唔會甩咁多<br />\n想mit都最好沖完熱水涼 啲皮軟少少先慢慢捽甩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連最佳嘅搣皮時機都知道得咁清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我淨係一隻腳有另一隻腳冇"},{"pid":"1ba68a13d77a155b4cd5ff2fa25491310693d3ac","tid":294070,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人知道用咩藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d710fbdd936c95dc68559cc027a94cd5c1009af9","tid":294070,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000e77cdf0172c6fa5f51f39be307a537846d38f","tid":294070,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T01:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人知道用咩藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甩皮使咩食藥咁誇張<br />\n你企喺度沖涼係咪偷懶唔洗腳板底呀？拎啲沖涼液用手捽，勤力啲，一個禮拜就好啦<br />\n問題持續先食藥啦"},{"pid":"929be934b412dbf426c576334fd0db72b8c2bc8c","tid":294070,"uid":33120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T01:16:46.000Z","msg":"間歇性病發"},{"pid":"aca5b710cc3135f9d0714f6bef1d29e453f4e5e0","tid":294070,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港地有香港腳</blockquote><br />\n但唔覺有痕，咁都係香港腳？</blockquote><br />\n甩皮係先兆 之後就生水泡就開始癢"}]}